WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.930 --> 00:00:02.510
&gt;&gt; Phoebe Connelly: We're going
to leave quite a bit of time

00:00:02.510 --> 00:00:05.360
after the presentation
for questions.

00:00:05.360 --> 00:00:06.660
So, about 15 minutes.

00:00:06.660 --> 00:00:08.740
There's microphones
in the aisles

00:00:08.740 --> 00:00:10.910
if you guys want to queue up.

00:00:10.910 --> 00:00:13.750
And, I have been asked to
remind you that if you come

00:00:13.750 --> 00:00:16.660
up to the microphone, you'll
be included in the videotape

00:00:16.660 --> 00:00:19.190
of the event, which may be
broadcast at a later date.

00:00:19.190 --> 00:00:21.610
So, you'll be preserved
for all time

00:00:21.610 --> 00:00:24.550
with your brilliant questions.

00:00:24.550 --> 00:00:27.310
It's my absolute pleasure
to introduce my guest,

00:00:27.310 --> 00:00:30.060
Sandhya Menon, author
of the two brilliant

00:00:30.060 --> 00:00:33.230
and successful YA novels,
When Dimple Met Rishi,

00:00:33.230 --> 00:00:35.510
